README.CSW
==========

Default locations
-----------------
Configuration directory: /etc/opt/csw.
Work directory: /var/opt/csw/dhcp.

Installation
------------
1. Modify the dhcpd.conf file in /etc/opt/csw.
2. Start DHCP with "/etc/init.d/cswdhcp start".

More info here: http://www.isc.org/products/DHCP/.


